"title": "6155: fall, of Adam and Eve",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "6155",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The first human beings abused their God-given freedom. Their original disobedience and resultant expulsion from the Garden of Eden is usually referred to as “the fall”.</p>\n<h2>The first sin was the disobedience of Adam and Eve to God's command</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:17\">GEN 2:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:1-Gen3:7\">GEN 3:1–3:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos6:7\">HOS 6:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:12\">ROM 5:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:14\">ROM 5:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:3\">2CO 11:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim2:14\">1TI 2:14</a></p>\n<h2>Causes of the fall</h2>\n<h3>Disobedience</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:16-Gen2:17\">GEN 2:16–2:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:1-Gen3:3\">GEN 3:1–3:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa43:27\">ISA 43:27</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos6:7\">HOS 6:7</a></p>\n<h3>Through satanic deception</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:4\">GEN 3:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:13\">GEN 3:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:3\">2CO 11:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim2:14\">1TI 2:14</a></p>\n<h3>Evil desire</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:6\">GEN 3:6</a></p>\n<h2>Adam and Eve tried to hide their disobedience</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:8-Gen3:13\">GEN 3:8–3:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job31:33\">JOB 31:33</a></p>\n<h2>The disobedience of Adam and Eve affected every relationship in life</h2>\n<h3>Relationship with God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:22-Gen3:23\">GEN 3:22–3:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen4:14\">GEN 4:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps90:3-Ps90:10\">PSA 90:3–90:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:20-Rom1:21\">ROM 1:20–1:21</a></p>\n<h3>Relationships among human beings</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:16\">GEN 3:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen4:1-Gen4:8\">GEN 4:1–4:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:18-Rom1:32\">ROM 1:18–1:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:1-Eph2:3\">EPH 2:1–2:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:11-Eph2:12\">EPH 2:11–2:12</a></p>\n<h3>The relationship between human beings and the creation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:17-Gen3:19\">GEN 3:17–3:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:14-Gen3:15\">GEN 3:14–3:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen4:10-Gen4:12\">GEN 4:10–4:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:19\">ROM 8:19</a></p>\n<h2>The consequences of the disobedience of Adam and Eve</h2>\n<h3>It leads to death and punishment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:12\">ROM 5:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:18\">ROM 1:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:21-1Cor15:22\">1CO 15:21–15:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess1:10\">1TH 1:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:14-1Thess2:16\">1TH 2:14–2:16</a></p>\n<h3>Sin springs from within the human mind, will and emotions</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:13-Jas1:15\">JAS 1:13–1:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:6-Jas4:7\">JAS 4:6–4:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:15-1John2:17\">1JN 2:15–2:17</a></p>",
